author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
The High Elves of Lothern and Chrace enter the Old World battlefields with their own army list variants, magic items and special Characters in this new kit-bash friendly supplement to Warhammer: The Old World. Let's check it out!

Thanks to Games Workshop for the complimentary copy of the book to review.
